author: bharath
msg: After purging acknowledged messages, if there are not more unacknowledges messsages for the given sequence, we completely remove the map entry for the sequence from the ResendCandidates map. The removal operation was buggy - The correct key was not being passed to the map remove method. As a result of this, the entry would forever stay in the map. Fixed this.
Also added a new test case for this. RetransmissionQueueImplTest#testPurgeAcknowledgedAll()
